snippet.title: Amber Heard is 'not facing a LAPD investigation for perjury in Johnny Depp's defamation case against
snippet.description:
Amber Heard is not being investigated for perjury in Johnny Depp's ongoing defamation case against her, according to her attorney.The 35-year-old actress's lawyer, Elaine Bredehoft, is denying reports that the Los Angeles Police Department is looking into whether she staged injuries and fabricated a crime scene following an alleged altercation between the former couple on May 20, 2016.'The statute of limitations for perjury in California is three years and has long since expired, so an investiga  ...
